{"tid":59963,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"輔助醫療職系應否學位化?","createTime":"2016-12-30T05:42:17.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-31T02:40:16.000Z","uid":61728,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"532b46af817db8d6b0e79112e2ba3237021f9806","tid":59963,"uid":61728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T05:42:17.000Z","msg":"現時學位職系職業唔多<br />\n最大路既只有教師、社工、言語治療師、營養師<br />\n三者即使唔升職，都享有緊POINT16-33既人工 (約29k-65k)<br />\n佢地拎唔拎得足係一回事，但事實上佢地薪酬理論上真係會有咁多<br />\n<br />\n但物理治療師、職業治療師、視光師同護士四者都只係拎緊文憑職系人工，頂薪大約只有45k<br />\n而前三者依家更只有學位畢業既人<br />\n要佢地拎文憑職系人工真係唔抵<br />\n<br />\n其實依四個職系專業性高，學位畢業比例大<br />\n實在係有資格拎學位職系人工"},{"pid":"16cb066970c14a40d200127f5679222c4a574d73","tid":59963,"uid":40979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T05:43:50.000Z","msg":"係香港講咩公平"},{"pid":"d0168e150a3702a701673d4d3f13f5a23b01d1e4","tid":59963,"uid":25221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T06:02:26.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6b8680636c78ed74adf762160aa400f9de8f6d4d","tid":59963,"uid":63190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T06:30:54.000Z","msg":"nurse有啲是nursing school出來都話呀<br />\nPT OT 視光全部大學出來都唔俾degree人工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"507170bb426bb9c1bad2b67ea0634488c1b4924f","tid":59963,"uid":204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T06:38:08.000Z","msg":"個標題應該係人工學位化<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7f5c4bd4e70483fe8040839bab291b35b6127d2","tid":59963,"uid":609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T06:58:22.000Z","msg":"屌 以偏概全<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nPT OT 有得升職架 大部分人做4~6年就升做一級物理/職業治療師 人工升一大截 仲高過社工同營養師好撚多 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"h